title: Beautiful New Community, Close to Schools, GREAT PRICE! Call Today!
posting_body: ['This beautiful new community is the perfect place to call home!', 'You can own this', 'GORGEOUS HOME', 'for only', '$1939/mo!*', 'We have simplified the home buying process for you.', 'Everything is done in our Sales Office, from writing your contract to closing and getting your keys!', 'Plus, we pay your closing costs when you finance with our approved Lender!', 'What are you waiting for?', 'Call TODAY for more info!', 'show contact info', 'x 300', 'The Avery Plan:', '🗝3 bedrooms', '🗝2.5 full bathrooms', '🗝Full Whirlpool Kitchen Appliance Suite', '🗝Walk in closet in the master bedroom', '🗝Loft Area', '🗝BRAND NEW CONSTRUCTION', '🗝Professionally Landscaped Yard', 'Click or call now to get started today!', 'show contact info', 'x 300', '*P&I.', 'Price $342,900, 5.625% Fixed/6.713% APR, 3.5% Down, FHA 30 Year, OAC from third party lender.', 'Other fees such as taxes, insurance, and HOA are not included in the sample monthly payment amount.', 'Prices and rates subject to change without notice.']
